      {
        "name": "Courier Availability Cache",
        "responsibility": "In-memory (per-instance) materialized view of available couriers with their last-known location and status. Rebuilt from DB on startup, kept warm via CDC/listen-notify. Used ONLY for candidate pre-filtering — never for assignment decisions.",
