      "decision": "PostgreSQL over a distributed database (CockroachDB, Spanner)",
      "gains": "Operational simplicity — the team already knows Postgres. Excellent tooling, monitoring, and community support. SELECT FOR UPDATE SKIP LOCKED is purpose-built for this workload. Single-digit millisecond transaction latency.",
